== 歷史 ==
=== 背景 ===
連接[[倫敦_(加拿大)|倫敦]]和咸美頓的道路一向是[[安大略省|安大略省]]的重要運輸走廊之一。[[美國獨立戰爭|美國獨立戰爭]]後，為了鞏固英國在[[上加拿大|上加拿大]]的控制權以及安置從美國遷居至此的保皇派人士，上加拿大總督閃高（{{lang|en|John Graves Simcoe}}）下令興建一條連接[[安大略湖|安大略湖]]西端（即庫提斯灣）和倫敦的道路，到1794年已開通至泰晤士河。此道路後來成為安大略省2號和5號公路一部分（省道資格後來被取消）<ref name="p11">Shragge p. 11</ref>。

連接[[多倫多|多倫多]]和咸美頓的中間道（{{lang|en|Middle Road}}）於1939年6月開通，來回行車線之間設有中央分隔帶，並與沿途其他道路立體交匯，是北美首條城際高速公路<ref>Stamp p. 12</ref>。安省公路廳計劃將倫敦和咸美頓之間的一段2號公路改建成與中間道相若的高速道路；胡士托以東的一段改建完畢，但隨著[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]展開，餘下路段的工程亦告擱置<ref name="JShragge" />。

=== 早期工程 ===
隨著[[韓戰|韓戰]]結束，安省公路工程亦重新上馬，而嶄新器材的應用亦足以抵消戰亂所造成的延誤<ref name="JShragge">{{cite web
 |title       = Highway 401 – The story
 |last        = Shragge
 |first       = John G.
 |year        = 2007
 |url         = http://www.roadscholar.on.ca/lateststory.html
 |accessdate  = February 12, 2010
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080328001341/http://www.roadscholar.on.ca/lateststory.html
 |archivedate = 2008年3月28日
 |deadurl     = yes
}}</ref>。[[安大略401號省道|401號公路]]為省府首要公路項目，倫敦至咸美頓高速公路項目退為其次。然而，兩者介乎倫敦和胡士托的路段實際上是重疊的，而該路段亦於1957年5月31日開通<ref>Ministry of Transportation and Communications pp. 8–9</ref>。另外，當局早於1954年已就胡士托和咸美頓之間的路段展開規劃程序<ref>{{cite news
 |title        = 4-Lane Road Start Seen
 |author       = Canadian Press
 |work         = The Ottawa Citizen
 |date         = July 9, 1954
 |page         = 2
 |volume       = 112
 |issue        = 9
 |url          = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RSEvAAAAIBAJ&sjid=od0FAAAAIBAJ&dq=hamilton%20expressway%20toronto&pg=5770%2C1363721
 |accessdate   = October 20, 2010
 |archive-date = 2022-04-23
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20220423061844/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RSEvAAAAIBAJ&sjid=od0FAAAAIBAJ&dq=hamilton%20expressway%20toronto&pg=5770%2C1363721
}}</ref>，到1958年已進行得如火如荼<ref>{{cite report

 | title      = Annual Report for the Fiscal Year
 | publisher  = Ontario Department of Highways
 | date       = March 31, 1958
 | url        = http://books.google.com/books?id=6f8iAQAAIAAJ&dq=Ontario+King%27s+Highways&q=C.A.H+403#search_anchor
 | accessdate = July 25, 2010}}</ref>。介乎[[伊利沙伯皇后道|伊利沙伯皇后道]]（QEW）和朗活士道（{{lang|en|Longwoods Road}}），長{{convert|9.0|km|mi}}的403號公路路段於1963年12月1日率先開通<ref name="dates" />，而延至鴨巴甸大道（{{lang|en|Aberdeen Avenue}}）的{{convert|3.7|km|mi}}路段則於1965年7月9日通車<ref name="dates">Department of Highways p. 11</ref>。

從鴨巴甸大道經尼亞加拉懸崖邊緣往安卡斯特與2號公路交匯的路段於1969年落成，原定於同年8月22日舉行剪綵儀式<ref>{{cite press release

 | title     = Highway 403 Opening on Wednesday August 27th
 | author    = Information Section
 | publisher = Department of Highways
 | date      = August 21, 1969}}</ref>。然而，沿線居民不滿公路旁沒有裝設圍欄以防兒童誤闖公路，省府因此在公路旁加設臨時護欄，並將剪綵儀式押後至同月27日舉行。居民仍不滿此安排並繼續抗議，剪綵儀式亦告取消<ref>{{cite news

 | title     = Residents Win Round Two in Battle of the 403
 | work      = The Hamilton Spectator
 | date      = August 27, 1969}}</ref>。公路廳長在翌周與居民會面並達成協議，在永久性護欄完工前當局將派員24小時在公路旁守候，以保兒童安全。該路段終在同年9月3日在沒有任何慶祝活動的情況下通車<ref>{{cite press release

 | title     = Highway 403, Opening
 | author    = Information Section
 | publisher = Department of Highways
 | date      = September 2, 1969}}</ref>，而403號公路咸美頓段亦告完成<ref>{{cite journal

 | title     = Proceedings of the... Convention
 | author    = A.T.C. McNab
 | publisher = Canadian Good Roads Association
 | year      = 1969
 | section   = Ontario
 | page      = 64}}</ref>。

另一方面，從北面繞過[[布蘭特福德|布蘭特福德]]市，長{{convert|10.3|km|mi}}的路段則於1966年10月31日開通<ref name="dates" />，但此布蘭特福德繞道在往後20多年並未與403號公路其他路段連貫起來<ref name="1987 map" />。

=== 密西沙加段 ===
[[File:Highway_403_End.jpg|thumb]]
403號公路[[密西沙加|密西沙加]]段的規劃工序於1950年代展開。計劃中的403號公路在皮爾縣（即今[[皮爾區|皮爾區]]）和[[大多倫多市|大多倫多市]]的界線駁上大多市政府擬建的列治圍高速公路（{{lang|en|Richview Expressway}}）<ref>Toronto transportation plan, 1959</ref>，並在此與[[安大略401號省道|401號]]和[[安大略427號省道|427號公路]]交匯。省府並於1962年在安省水電公司從布靈頓伸延至怡陶碧谷溪的電線通道旁預留空間，待日後興建公路<ref name="troublefree">{{cite news

 | title   = 403: A Trouble-Free Way
 | first   = Brace
 | last    = Ward
 | work    = The Toronto Star
 | date    = January 4, 1981
 | page    = A16
 | quote   = It was designated in 1962, when traffic studies showed that additional "freeway capacity" would be required to handle traffic volumes between Hamilton and Toronto.}}</ref>。安省公路廳再於1965年5月25日公佈《多倫多地區西部公路規劃研究》，計劃將403號公路從布靈頓往東北伸延至401號和27號公路的交匯處<ref>{{cite news

 | title    = 700 Million Freeways West of Metro
 | work     = Globe and Mail
 | location = Toronto
 | date     = May 26, 1966
 | volume   = 123
 | issue    = 36,335
 | section  = News
 | pages    = 1, 25
 | quote    = The program calls for construction of a 23-mile section of Highway 403, from Burlington to the Macdonald-Cartier Freeway, west of Highway 27; a 12-mile freeway from Belfield Drive in Etobicoke, running northwesterly around Brampton to Georgetown; and a five-mile freeway from Richview Road in Etobicoke to Woodbridge.}}</ref>。

然而，往後年間多倫多市民反對在市内興建高速公路的呼聲漸高，列治圍高速公路項目因而取消，而403號公路密西沙加段的東端亦因此往西遷移，在密西沙加東北部與401號公路和擬建的[[安大略410號省道|410號公路]]交匯<ref>{{cite news

 | title    = Drivers Will Wait Years Before Relief from QEW Jams
 | first    = Thomas
 | last     = Coleman
 | work     = Globe and Mail
 | location = Toronto
 | date     = July 12, 1975
 | volume   = 132
 | issue    = 39,185
 | section  = News
 | pages    = 5}}</ref>；該段401號公路因此需從來回6線行車擴濶至12線行車。公路西端則改為於皮爾區和[[荷頓區|荷頓區]]的界線與QEW交匯，以舒緩QEW密西沙加段的交通流量。省府將修改後的項目計劃交予密西沙加市議會，並於1977年12月獲密市議會通過，工程隨之展開<ref>{{cite news

 | title   = Doubts Raised About Route of New 403
 | first   = Frank
 | last    = Calleja
 | work    = The Toronto Star
 | date    = November 8, 1979
 | page    = A19}}</ref>。

403號公路密西沙加段在1980年代初分階段通車。介乎401號公路和哥富拿道的路段於1980年8月18日率先開通<ref>{{cite news

 | title   = New Highway Opens
 | work    = Toronto Daily Star
 | date    = August 18, 1980
 | page    = A13
 | quote   = A new 3.6-kilometre stretch of Highway 403 was to be opened to traffic this morning, as part of a plan to divert traffic from the Queen Elizabeth Way through Mississauga. The new section will run from Highway 401 southbound to the Eglinton-Cawthra Rd. interchange.}}</ref>，而介乎QEW和[[登打士街_(安大略省)|登打士街]]的路段則於1981年中通車，再於同年11月17日延至愛蓮妙斯園林路（{{lang|en|Erin Mills Parkway}}）<ref name="1981opening">{{cite news

 | title   = Highway 403 Section Open to Traffic Today
 | first   = Brian
 | last    = Dexter
 | work    = The Toronto Star
 | date    = November 17, 1981
 | page    = A18
 | quote   = It runs west from Erin Mills Parkway north of Burnhamthorpe Road, to Highway 5 in Oakville, where a spur to the Queen Elizabeth Way at Ford Drive has been used by traffic for several months.}}</ref>。介乎愛蓮妙斯園林路和哥富拿道的路段需透過兩條橋樑跨越克萊迪特河谷，因此工程需時更長，待1982年12月2日才開通。403號公路密西沙加段全長{{convert|22|km|mi}}，耗資8700萬元興建<ref>{{cite news

 | title   = $87 Million Highway 403 Complete As Last Leg Opens
 | work    = The Toronto Star
 | date    = December 2, 1982
 | page    = A18}}</ref>。

安省運輸廳同期開始研究改建介乎聯福徑（{{lang|en|Renforth Drive}}）和403號公路的一段401號公路，以及介乎401號公路和10號公路（現曉倫大略街）的一段403號公路，將上述路段的行車線以護欄分流為短途線和長途線（{{lang|en|collector-express system}}）<ref name="planning">{{cite news

 | title    = Ontario Government Notice
 | work     = The Globe and Mail
 | location = Toronto
 | date     = February 17, 1982
 | section  = Classifieds
 | page     = C4
 | quote    = The Ministry of Transportation and Communications has undertaken a Preliminary Design Study to examine the upgrading of Highway 401 from Renforth Drive to Second Line West and Highway 403 from Highway 401 to Highway 10. The Preliminary Design Study has also examined the construction of the Highway 403 Extension, from Cawthra Rd. to Dixie Rd. In the mid 1970's some preliminary planning was completed for an express-collectors system on Highway 401 and 403 within Mississauga.}}</ref>。工程從1982年末至1985年夏季進行；固有從403號公路通往401號公路東行線的匝道成為短途線交通專用，而當局則於交匯處之内加建兩條天橋供長途線交通來往兩條公路<ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1983–1984<!-- April 1983 -->
 | page      = XI
 | issn      = 0714-1149}}</ref><ref name="1985c" />。

原有預留給403號公路，介乎哥富拿道和怡陶碧谷溪的空間最終改建成市級的東門園林路（{{lang|en|Eastgate Parkway}}）。項目規劃工序於1982年展開<ref name="planning" /><ref>{{cite book

 | title     = 403 Arterial Extension
 | first     = C.
 | last      = Meyers
 | publisher = City of Mississauga Planning Department
 | year      = 1986}}</ref>，1988年至1994年間施工<ref>{{cite news

 | title    = Highway Extension May Ensure More Development, Report Says
 | first    = Mike
 | last     = Funston
 | work     = The Toronto Star
 | date     = May 20, 1986
 | section  = Neighbors West
 | page     = 6}}</ref>。首期介乎哥富拿道和狄斯道（{{lang|en|Dixie Road}}）的路段於1991年初開通<ref>{{cite news

 | title    = Opening Extension of 403 Can Improve Traffic Flow
 | first    = Mike
 | last     = Funston
 | work     = The Toronto Star
 | date     = January 10, 1991
 | section  = Neighbors West
 | page     = 3}}</ref>，而介乎狄斯道和[[艾靈頓大道|艾靈頓大道]]的路段則於1994年末通車<ref>{{cite news

 | title    = Eastgate Extension Boon to Motorists
 | first    = Warren
 | last     = Potter
 | work     = The Toronto Star
 | date     = October 27, 1994
 | section  = Mississauga
 | page     = MS3}}</ref>。

